Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also compares the performance of different deep learning models, which involves training and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the use of deep learning models for generating text involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also discusses the efficiency and performance of the explored models, which could fall under the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SD).
